{"tid":2134404,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何韻詩不屑：爭取女權，要在方便自己的時候","createTime":"2020-07-31T16:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T00:09:01.000Z","uid":44730,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dded8ed500d2179393f59b16b8c43a7823c2cf5c","tid":2134404,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T16:31:23.000Z","msg":"近期社交平台IG吹起一遍「women empowerment」挑戰熱潮，紛紛在IG上載黑白相，以支持女性權利，劉鑾雄太太甘比、千億新抱徐子淇、李嘉欣等都有表態參與。<br />\n<br />\n不過有關今次挑戰的起源，卻有不同的說法，有指是源自土耳其一宗男友殺害女友的案件，但被有關當局冷淡處理，由於女死者的黑白相頻密出現在當地傳媒上，所以有人發起「women empowerment」挑戰活動，為女死者討回公道。"},{"pid":"5ddf0f808744da5619acd30986a9e8209b77635b","tid":2134404,"uid":44730,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T16:31:36.000Z","msg":"另外，亦有指是藉黑白相增加公眾對癌症的關注，尤其是女患者及其照顧者，也有指是為全球抗疫打氣。<br />\n<br />\n網上亦有文章討論今次「women empowerment」挑戰熱潮，當中批評參與「women empowerment」的人，「澳洲山火時你們熱切為樹熊禱告，但滿街二噁英時也不見你們之間誰站過出來說影響生態」，並配上多位於去年香港抗爭運動中，受傷甚至死亡的女性黑白相片。"},{"pid":"e857198882b6e97d018a2d6940adaee779ef27cb","tid":2134404,"uid":44730,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T16:31:54.000Z","msg":"歌手何韻詩也轉載相關文章，並留言「We want women empowerment! (But only when it is convenient for us.) 」，明顯睇唔過眼一眾未有了解挑戰背後動機之餘，只識「趁墟」及po靚相呃like的港女。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民認為何韻詩「講得好」，短短一小時已有超過2,400個讚好，而且亦有網民留言「炫耀係名媛專業呀」，寸到應一應。"},{"pid":"6acaaa1ad2b79324f05ff1f5c13fe0ecf282c0d3","tid":2134404,"uid":44730,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200731/1536pix/1596187852_6aa8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200731%2F1536pix%2F1596187852_6aa8.jpg&h=3fafbd01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n何韻詩分享「women empowerment」的文章，不屑有些人只為了方便才表態。"},{"pid":"4800dd7707e9196b87d42b0f8ce8a209828e7a3a","tid":2134404,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200731/1536pix/1596187855_072d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200731%2F1536pix%2F1596187855_072d.jpg&h=57351c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少名人都有參與「women empowerment」挑戰，當中包括劉鑾雄太太甘比。"},{"pid":"27f7d1d353f446321741b5c29d6c8a9aab572378","tid":2134404,"uid":280853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dded8ed500d2179393f59b16b8c43a7823c2cf5c","tid":2134404,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T16:31:23.000Z","msg":"近期社交平台IG吹起一遍「women empowerment」挑戰熱潮，紛紛在IG上載黑白相，以支持女性權利，劉鑾雄太太甘比、千億新抱徐子淇、李嘉欣等都有表態參與。<br />\n<br />\n不過有關今次挑戰的起源，卻有不同的說法，有指是源自土耳其一宗男友殺害女友的案件，但被有關當局冷淡處理，由於女死者的黑白相頻密出現在當地傳媒上，所以有人發起「women empowerment」挑戰活動，為女死者討回公道。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T16:33:51.000Z","msg":"食屎啦班虛偽臭閪"},{"pid":"021976da55446cf002b424ec7ef1638ff97cfadd","tid":2134404,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T16:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200731/1536pix/1596187857_3419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200731%2F1536pix%2F1596187857_3419.jpg&h=b212aeb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李嘉欣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200731/1536pix/1596187861_1ab7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200731%2F1536pix%2F1596187861_1ab7.jpg&h=3792cffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n千億新抱徐子淇"},{"pid":"a9b54f399bf8f94b5af2013f195a45ec462c5a2b","tid":2134404,"uid":1251,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T16:34:44.000Z","msg":"靠個西發達既爭取女權寧舍有說服力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6030bfd7605e15feb559666356fdaf9c53998de6","tid":2134404,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43a7dc7317